```plantuml
@startuml IBM_datastax-cassandra-clickstream

actor User
participant "Next.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Next.js API Routes" as API
participant "clicks.service.js" as Service
participant "DataStax/Cassandra" as Database

User -> Frontend: Browse products
Frontend -> API: GET /api/products/[category]
API -> Service: getProducts()
Service -> Database: Query products
Database --> Service: Product data
Service --> API: Product data
API --> Frontend: Product data
Frontend -> User: Display products

User -> Frontend: Add to cart
Frontend -> API: POST /api/products/index (addToCart)
API -> Service: addToCart(eventData)
Service -> Database: Insert clickstream event
Database --> Service: ACK
Service --> API: Success
API --> Frontend: Success
Frontend -> User: Update cart UI

User -> Frontend: View history
Frontend -> API: GET /api/history
API -> Service: getActivity(userId)
Service -> Database: Query clickstream
Database --> Service: Clickstream data
Service --> API: Clickstream data
API --> Frontend: Clickstream data
Frontend -> User: Display history

User -> Frontend: Authenticate
Frontend -> API: POST /api/auth/[...nextauth]
API -> Service: (auth handled by NextAuth)
Service --> API: Auth response
API --> Frontend: Auth status
Frontend -> User: Update auth UI

@enduml
```